stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Clean
    Clean --> Loaded: rising TC / entropy
    Loaded --> Overheating: low budget + high claim pressure
    Overheating --> Breach: unsafe operator selected
    Breach --> RecoveryOnly: recovery gate
    RecoveryOnly --> Loaded: evidence or budget restored
    Loaded --> Clean: lower-cost closure
    Overheating --> Loaded: downgrade / clarify / hold

    note right of Clean
      broad operator set
      normal claim strength
    end note

    note right of Overheating
      forbid strong anchors
      require uncertainty or recheck
    end note

    note right of Breach
      output cannot be treated as evidence
      recovery-only actions
    end note
